  "detailed_description": "Step into the Polydome. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nPolyDome is a musical environment that changes and progresses when you interact with it. Think of it as a sequencer, but rather than being a tool for creating music, it's a place where you can explore and create different musical phrases and sounds. The point of PolyDome is not to win, loose or compete, but simply to relax and enjoy.",
